  <brief_title>Response of Desloratadine Syrup in the Relief of Symptoms Associated With Perennial Allergic Rhinitis in Pediatric Patients (Study P04299)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Observational Study Evaluating the Safety and Efficacy of Desloratadine Syrup for Perennial Allergic Rhinitis in Indonesian Pediatric Patients</official_title>
